column2: How unfortunate it did not sink...
My reign will truly last ten thousand years!
Maybe I should launch an expedition...
A shame the island was lost...
A shame the island was lost...
A pity only the island sank...
Do you really expect me to believe this nonsense?
These tales can't be true... right?
